# ===== NEW CONFIGURATION SYSTEM =====
# The application now supports comprehensive configuration management
# Configuration sources (in order of priority):
#   1. Environment variables (highest priority)
#   2. config.{environment}.yaml (e.g., config.production.yaml)
#   3. config.yaml (base configuration)
#   4. Default values (lowest priority)
#
# Configuration Features:
#   - Hot reload support in development mode
#   - Environment-specific overrides
#   - Validation and type safety
#   - Feature flags with dynamic updates
#
# Configuration File Path
CONFIG_PATH=config/config.yaml  # Path to configuration file
#
# To use configuration files:
#   1. Copy config/config.yaml as your base
#   2. Create config/config.production.yaml for production overrides
#   3. Set APP_ENV=production to load production config
#
# Note: Environment variables always override config file values
